quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"(Saad). By the Quran, having the reminder"
  38,2,Yet those who disbelieve are in self-admiration and opposition
  38,3,"How many of a generation did We destroy before them, and they called out (for help) and it was too late to escape"
  38,4,"And they were surprised that a warner came to them from them, and the disbelievers said: this is a lying magician"
  38,5,Did he make the gods into one god? This is certainly a strange thing
  38,6,"And the leaders of them went off (saying): go on and persevere about your gods, indeed this is certainly something wanted (and expected from you)"
  38,7,"We did not hear this in the previous faith, this is only an invention"
  38,8,"Was the reminder (only) sent down to him among us? No, they are in doubt about My reminder, rather they have not tasted My punishment"
  38,9,Or the treasures of mercy of your Master the powerful and the giver are with them
  38,10,Or do they have the rule of the skies and the earth and whatever between them? (If they do) then they should go up by the means (they have)
  38,11,They are a defeated army of the coalitions in there
  38,12,People of Noah and Aad and Pharaoh the owners of the stakes (pyramids) denied before them
  38,13,"And Thamud and people of Lot and the inhabitants of the woods (people of Shu'aib), they were the coalitions (that denied the messengers)"
  38,14,"They all denied the messengers, so they deserved My punishment"
  38,15,"And these are only awaiting a single awesome roar, which there would not be any delay for it (or any comeback)"
  38,16,"And they said: our Master, rush our share (of punishment) for us before the day of accounting"